						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Some&nbsp;SPaG&nbsp;recommendations</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Some&nbsp;SPaG&nbsp;recommendations</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <blockquote> <p>We need to neutralize SCP-5808-2 not disguise it.</p> </blockquote> <p>into</p> <blockquote> <p>We need to neutralize SCP-5808-2<strong>,</strong> not disguise it.</p> </blockquote> <hr /> <blockquote> <p>Place SCP-5808-1 in a Relativity Exclusion Zone in order to severe the connect to SCP-5808-2.</p> </blockquote> <p>into</p> <blockquote> <p>Place SCP-5808-1 in a Relativity Exclusion Zone in order to severe the <strong>connection</strong> to SCP-5808-2.</p> </blockquote> </div> </div> </div> <p>Great article, the ending really bumps it from &quot;good&quot; to &quot;damn good&quot;. +1.</p> 
